<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Question Reply</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .email-header {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .email-footer {
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
        }
        a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>New Reply to Your Question</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Dear <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>
            <p>There is a new reply to your question regarding <strong><%= title %></strong>.</p>
            <p>Please visit the platform to check the reply and continue the discussion.</p>
            <p>Thank you!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Your Company. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p><a href="https://yourwebsite.com">Visit our website</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
